Subject: [PATCH 0860/1221] =?UTF-8?q?MLK-11206:=20input:=20misc:=20fxls8471:?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20support=20=C2=B12g/=C2=B14g/=C2=B18g=20dynamically=20selection?=
